140
00:09:34,260 --> 00:09:35,420
Master…

141
00:09:35,420 --> 00:09:37,860
Xiao Gang! Xiao Gang…

142
00:09:37,860 --> 00:09:39,040
Master!

143
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:40,840
- How are you feeling, Xiao Gang?
- Master!

144
