Damn it! Martial Soul Hall…

146
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:46,000
Little San, I’m sorry for your suffering.

147
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:48,060
Dean, I’m okay.

148
00:11:48,060 --> 00:11:51,320
I’m okay with anything as long as Xiao Wu can be revived.

149
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:53,840
What are you planning to do here this time?

150
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:56,360
I’m planning to do some training

151
