178
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:41,520
<i>Tang Clan. I can only miss you in this way now.</i>

179
00:15:41,520 --> 00:15:43,920
Brother San, you’re setting up a clan by your own.

180
00:15:43,920 --> 00:15:46,640
